org.apache.oodt.cas.product.jaxrs.services

Class CasProductJaxrsService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.oodt.cas.product.jaxrs.services.CasProductJaxrsService

  • public class CasProductJaxrsService
extends Object
    Service class that handles HTTP requests and returns file manager entities such as references and products as JAX-RS resources converted to different formats.
    Version:
    $Revision$
    Author:
    rlaidlaw
